divs: Sighting DetailsSeen lights above me flashing then golden lights floating down landing on me it was penetrating it felt good it was fun I then looked at one the lights it was like afire fly I looked at it closely it had eyes and a mouth then it spoke it freaked me out a bit I was only about seven years old I'm over fifty now I told my little sister it spoke but we just kept having fun these little fire flys felt good we ended in on the side of the house then I started hearing some one talking to me in my head and I could talk back just by my thoughts I ask who they were they said they where explorers there was a father a mother a son and a daughter and some one like general or pertector they made three boxes out of light in front of me all joined together it was like movie the past the present and the future mean while my sister is playing with there son there daughter is shey there's a lot more to my story they told us if we told any one they would come back and get us some of them wanted us to go with them now but the mother said no she was the one talked to the most she was like the virgin marry to me
